Version 3.11.3
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Released: 2013-12-17

* Translations
 - Updated Brazilian Portuguese translation (Rafael Ferreira)
 - Updated Dutch translation (Erwin Poeze, Reinout van Schouwen)
 - Updated Greek translation (Dimitris Spingos)
 - Updated Russian translation (Yuri Myasoedov)
 - Updated Spanish translation (Daniel Mustieles)
 - Updated Tajik translation (Victor Ibragimov)
 - Updated Tamil translation (Shantha kumar)
 - Updated Thai translation (Akom Chotiphantawanon)

* New Features:
 - Remove catalog support (Richard Hughes)
 - Remove the service pack support (Richard Hughes)

* Bugfix:
 - Do not use deprecated libpackagekit functionality (Richard Hughes)
 - Do not use the deprecated (and unused) PkMessage (Richard Hughes)
 - Do not use the deprecated (and unused) UpgradeSystem (Richard Hughes)
 - Fix compile with newer versions of PackageKit (Richard Hughes)
 - Never, ever, use Werror (Richard Hughes)
 - Standardize Help/About/Quit in the app menu (Michael Catanzaro)

Version 3.11.1
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Released: 2013-11-05

* Translations
 - Added Brazilian Portuguese translation for help files (Rafael Ferreira)
 - Updated Brazilian Portuguese translation (Rafael Ferreira)
 - Updated Catalan (Valencian) translation (Carles Ferrando)
 - Updated Czech translation (Marek Černocký)
 - Updated Galician translations (Fran Diéguez)
 - Updated Italian translation (Gianvito Cavasoli)
 - Updated Slovenian translation (Matej Urbančič)
 - Updated Spanish translation (Daniel Mustieles)
 - Updated Tajik translation (Victor Ibragimov)
 - Updated Traditional Chinese translation (Chao-Hsiung Liao, Cheng-Chia Tseng)
 - Updated Turkish translation (Muhammet Kara)

* New (and removed) Features:
 - Modernise a few of the Glade files (Richard Hughes)
 - Remove gpk-distro-upgrade (Richard Hughes)
 - Remove the gpk-install-catalog binary (Richard Hughes)
 - Remove the gpk-install-mime-type binary (Richard Hughes)
 - Remove the gpk-install-package-name binary (Richard Hughes)
 - Remove the gpk-install-provide-file binary (Richard Hughes)
 - Remove the python helper functions (Richard Hughes)
 - Translate the AppData file (Richard Hughes)

* Bugfix:
 - Do not set gnome-settings-daemon schema in the prefs program (Richard Hughes)
 - Do not show a 'Check now' button in the prefs (Richard Hughes)
 - Do not show a critical warning when we try to remove a missing GSource (Richard Hughes)
 - Do not support ConsoleKit anymore for restart detection (Richard Hughes)
 - Do not use deprecated GTK symbols (Richard Hughes)
 - Do not use the DesktopDB in gpk-application (Richard Hughes)
 - Don't link to UPower as it is not needed by anything (Richard Hughes)
 - Fix the AppData name to be less generic (Richard Hughes)
 - Never pass relative paths to the session interface (Matthias Klumpp)
 - Remove EggDBusMonitor as it was basically unused (Richard Hughes)
 - Show the whole list in the window when showing repos (Richard Hughes)
 - Use 16:9 screenshots in the AppData files (Richard Hughes)

