Version 0.2.2
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Released: 2008-06-05

* Translations
 - Add Russian translation (Leonid Kanter)
 - Updated Spanish translation (Daniel Mustieles)
 - Updated Norwegian bokmål translation (Kjartan Maraas)
 - Update polish translation (Wadim Dziedzic)
